    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that balances dependable performance with exceptional value. This unit has undergone a comprehensive inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and long-term reliability. Offering a refined driving experience and a clean aesthetic, it stands as a testament to consistent care and responsible ownership. Secure this high-caliber selection at a competitive market rate.",
