    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey! I'm parting ways with my absolute favorite ride. It\u2019s been so reliable and still looks great on the road! It\u2019s in solid shape and totally ready for its next adventure. I\u2019ve taken really nice care of it, and I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
